                        <h3><a href="#">Financial Disclosures/Conflicts of Interest</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>At the start of the guideline development process all Guideline Committee (GC) members'
interests were recorded on a standard declaration form that covered
consultancies, fee-paid work, share-holdings, fellowships and support
from the healthcare industry. At all subsequent GC meetings, members
declared new, arising conflicts of interest which were always recorded
(see Appendix F in the full guideline appendices [see the "Availability
of Companion Documents" field]).</p></div></p>
